title: Heather Storm of "Garage Squad"
description:
Heather Storm is a TV personality and co-host of the Velocity show, "Garage Squad." She also road trips her '65 Mustang around America in a travel series, "Drive Yourself Local". 

Learn more about the show at: https://garagesquad.tv/

This show is also a video, with assets paired to the conversation: https://youtu.be/Krt3SJpq4DI
